node.title: Search on for swimmer missing in Waikato River
node.description: Police say emergency services received a report of a missing swimmer shortly after 6pm.
node.content:
["Searchers are trying to find a swimmer missing in the Waikato River.", "", "
\nPhoto: 123rf\n
", "Police say emergency services received a report of a missing swimmer shortly after 6pm.", "Police are coordinating the search.", "They say initial reports indicate a group of four people went into the water but only three returned to shore.", "A Westpac Rescue Helicopter crew has not found any sign, and searches by boat and jet ski downriver towards Claudelands Bridge were continuing until dark."]
